name: Plumble
tagline: A powerful, slick, and easy to use Mumble client for Android.
body:
Plumble is an enhanced Mumble client for Android with the goal of replicating the full functionality of the desktop version. It is available for purchase on Google's Play store. All proceeds go to furthering development of the app.

[Get Plumble]("https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.morlunk.mumbleclient")

See this page on the wiki for compilation instructions, if you'd like to help with development or just compile your own copy gratis :)

[Building Plumble](https://github.com/Morlunk/Plumble/wiki/Building-Plumble)

If you'd like, you can donate to me via PayPal below.

[Donate](https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=U33T852KAR9PG)
